snippet.title: Run-N-Jump-N-Jump-N-Run LAUNCH TRAILER
snippet.description:
Run-N-Jump-N-Jump-N-Run is AVAILABLE NOW for free at Game Jolt!

Follow @MansterSoft on twitter for the latest news and updates.

Jump through treacherous obstacles atop your trusty Horsey in this one-button ASCII Runner. When that gets boring you can make and save your own level using the World's Simplest Level Builder.

Get it today!

https://gamejolt.com/games/run-n-jump/279324
http://manstersoft.com
https://twitter.com/manstersoft
